data.title: 'Enakkul Oruvan': Audience review
data.meta_description: Within hours after the movie hit the screens today, audience are already going ga-ga over Siddharth's performance.. Movie Review.  Film Review.  Cinema Review
data.text:
Enakkul Oruvan is the official remake of the Kannada movie Lucia and marks Siddharth's return after the success of Jigarthanda. It is a psychological thriller, presented in a convincing manner.

Within hours after the movie hit the screens today, audience are already going ga-ga over Siddharth's performance. Check out what few movie buffs had to say:

Many have applauded Santhosh Narayanan's background score suiting well to almost all the scenes effortlessly.

The cinematography by Gopi Amarnath seems to be a big plus point for the movie.

The screenplay seems to be a bit complicated as it confuses the general audience in between.
